---
title: Herby Pork Sausage & Apple Slaw Subs with Wedges, Dill-Parsley Mayo & Onion Chutney
description: Bangers in a bun, it’s hot dogs done up to the nines tonight! Fill up your buns with herby pork sausages, a fragrant creamy layer
of herby mayo and a sweet apple slaw. Serve with wedges to finish off this upgraded classic.
